Yƒµc<?php exit; ?>a:1:{s:7:"content";a:24:{s:10:"_edit_last";a:1:{i:0;s:1:"1";}s:10:"_edit_lock";a:1:{i:0;s:12:"1672838157:1";}s:17:"_wp_page_template";a:1:{i:0;s:7:"default";}s:19:"site-sidebar-layout";a:1:{i:0;s:7:"default";}s:19:"site-content-layout";a:1:{i:0;s:7:"default";}s:29:"theme-transparent-header-meta";a:1:{i:0;s:7:"default";}s:20:"_elementor_edit_mode";a:1:{i:0;s:7:"builder";}s:24:"_elementor_template_type";a:1:{i:0;s:7:"wp-post";}s:18:"_elementor_version";a:1:{i:0;s:5:"3.9.2";}s:22:"_elementor_pro_version";a:1:{i:0;s:5:"3.8.1";}s:15:"_eael_custom_js";a:1:{i:0;s:0:"";}s:24:"_elementor_page_settings";a:1:{i:0;s:57:"a:1:{s:18:"eael_ext_toc_title";s:17:"Table of Contents";}";}s:15:"_elementor_data";a:1:{i:0;s:11882:"[{"id":"858fae6","elType":"section","settings":{"eae_slider_delay":"5000","gradient_color_list":[{"eae_animated_gradient_color":"#00a6d8","_id":"376d554"},{"eae_animated_gradient_color":"#b800c9","_id":"d97294d"},{"eae_animated_gradient_color":"#e57600","_id":"774c993"}],"z_index":0},"elements":[{"id":"8af7f3a","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":100,"_inline_size":null,"eae_slider_delay":"5000","gradient_color_list":[{"eae_animated_gradient_color":"#00a6d8","_id":"6a69d0c"},{"eae_animated_gradient_color":"#b800c9","_id":"374a59b"},{"eae_animated_gradient_color":"#e57600","_id":"e8868f6"}]},"elements":[{"id":"c0da878","elType":"widget","settings":{"editor":"<p>On the 2nd of December (IANS), Flipkart and Polygon, which is a blockchain platform based on Ethereum, announced their intentions to construct a center of excellence (CoE) in India.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>This would make it possible to learn more about and build Web3 and metaverse commerce use cases.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>At this point, both the making and the use of decentralized technologies are in their early stages.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p>","text_color":"#333333","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Proxima Nova Alt Reg","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":18,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"400","typography_line_height":{"unit":"em","size":1.3,"sizes":[]}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"},{"id":"1c90645","elType":"widget","settings":{"title":"How will this partnership have an impact?","align":"center","title_color":"#000000","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Proxima Nova Alt Semi-Bold","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":30,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"600","typography_line_height":{"unit":"em","size":1.2,"sizes":[]},"header_size":"p"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"heading"},{"id":"01b56e5","elType":"widget","settings":{"editor":"<p>In a joint statement, the companies talked about how everyone can use Web 3.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>The CTO of the e-commerce site Flipkart, Jeyandran Venugopal, said, \"Flipkart joins Polygon to launch the metaverse.\"<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>We're happy to work with Polygon to show our users the advantages of Web3, Metaverse commerce, and Web3 in general.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Through the partnership with Polygon, Flipkart is invited to join a lively community of other projects that use the same platform.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Polygon has become the platform of choice for a number of important Web3 projects, like <strong>OpenSea<\/strong> and <strong>Aave<\/strong>, as well as companies like <strong>Starbucks<\/strong>, <strong>Stripe<\/strong>, and <strong>Meta<\/strong>.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>This is because Polygon has low network costs, fast transaction speeds, and no environmental impact.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Flipkart Labs was started this year with the goal of coming up with new ideas that could change the way people shop online in India.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>In particular, Flipkart Labs has been looking at non-fungible tokens (NFTs).<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Virtual immersive stores, and other uses of blockchain technology in Web3 and metaverse commerce.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p>","text_color":"#333333","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Proxima Nova Alt Reg","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":18,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"400","typography_line_height":{"unit":"em","size":1.3,"sizes":[]}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"},{"id":"608eba1","elType":"widget","settings":{"title":"Flipkart created FireDrops.","align":"left","title_color":"#000000","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Proxima Nova Alt Semi-Bold","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":22,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"600","typography_line_height":{"unit":"em","size":1.2,"sizes":[]},"header_size":"h3"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"heading"},{"id":"345fb3b","elType":"widget","settings":{"editor":"<p>A clear NFT platform that refocuses the value of NFTs on essential services and gives businesses the freedom to try out different city-building activities<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Flipkart and eDAO worked together to make Flipverse, a metaverse shopping mall.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>It came out just in time for the Christmas shopping season.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Sandeep Nailwal, who helped start Polygon, has said that getting the next billion customers to use Web3 is very important to the company's success.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>The two companies will work together to \"drive R&amp;D at the point where Web3 and experiential retail meet,\" he says.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>We think that the Blockchain-eCommerce Center of Excellence will be a major factor in the growth of online business over the next few years.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p>","text_color":"#333333","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Proxima Nova Alt Reg","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":18,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"400","typography_line_height":{"unit":"em","size":1.3,"sizes":[]}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"},{"id":"06c0729","elType":"widget","settings":{"title":"Flipkart brings the Flipverse shopping experience to the world.","align":"left","title_color":"#000000","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Proxima Nova Alt Semi-Bold","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":22,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"600","typography_line_height":{"unit":"em","size":1.2,"sizes":[]},"header_size":"h3"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"heading"},{"id":"a192846","elType":"widget","settings":{"editor":"<p>Flipkart, an online store, has created Flipverse, a Flipkart metaverse shopping environment, just for Android users.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Several companies have teamed up with Flipkart metaverse technology to make this kind of web-based shopping possible.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Puma<\/strong> makes shoes and sportswear, Noise is a fashion brand, Nivea makes cosmetics, Lavie makes handbags, and TVS makes motorcycles.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p>","text_color":"#333333","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Proxima Nova Alt Reg","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":18,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"400","typography_line_height":{"unit":"em","size":1.3,"sizes":[]}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"},{"id":"ce700c1","elType":"widget","settings":{"title":"What kinds of activities are available on Flipkart's Flipverse?","align":"left","title_color":"#000000","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Proxima Nova Alt Semi-Bold","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":22,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"600","typography_line_height":{"unit":"em","size":1.2,"sizes":[]},"header_size":"h3"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"heading"},{"id":"5c259b7","elType":"widget","settings":{"editor":"<p>Shop in a photorealistic virtual shopping experience that is created in 3D.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>In a world of virtual shopping, you may \"talk\" with the stores and restaurants you like most by using an avatar that you have customized.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Take part in contests hosted by brands.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Get access to exclusive discounts.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>NFTs may be exchanged for other digital assets. Amass supercoins.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p>","text_color":"#333333","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Proxima Nova Alt Reg","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":18,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"400","typography_line_height":{"unit":"em","size":1.3,"sizes":[]}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"},{"id":"144b50d","elType":"widget","settings":{"title":"How you can join the Flipverse","align":"center","title_color":"#000000","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Proxima Nova Alt Semi-Bold","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":30,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"600","typography_line_height":{"unit":"em","size":1.2,"sizes":[]}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"heading"},{"id":"3c66ec4","elType":"widget","settings":{"editor":"<p>1. Firedrops by Flipkart is a virtual world that you can explore by opening the app on a computer and clicking \"Enter Flipverse.\"<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>2. Please use your mobile device to read the QR code.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>3. At this point, the FireDrops app would start up.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>4. Go to Flipverse, make a profile, and give yourself a name and a picture.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>5. Now you're in the Flipverse.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p>","text_color":"#333333","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Proxima Nova Alt Reg","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":18,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"400","typography_line_height":{"unit":"em","size":1.3,"sizes":[]}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"},{"id":"2bc7477","elType":"widget","settings":{"title":"Brand lists that can be bought in the Flipverse","align":"center","title_color":"#000000","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Proxima Nova Alt Semi-Bold","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":30,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"600","typography_line_height":{"unit":"em","size":1.2,"sizes":[]},"header_size":"h3"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"heading"},{"id":"b64527e","elType":"widget","settings":{"editor":"<p>Several companies have teamed up with Flipkart virtual shopping to make this kind of web-based shopping possible.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Puma<\/strong> makes shoes and sportswear, <strong>Noise<\/strong> is a fashion brand, <strong>Nivea<\/strong> makes cosmetics, <strong>Lavie<\/strong> makes handbags, and <strong>TVS<\/strong> makes motorcycles.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>There are also vendors like <strong>Campus<\/strong>,<strong> VIP<\/strong>,<strong> Himalaya<\/strong>,<strong> Ajmal Perfumes<\/strong>,<strong> Butterfly India<\/strong>, and <strong>Tokyo Talkies<\/strong>.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p>","text_color":"#333333","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Proxima Nova Alt Reg","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":18,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"400","typography_line_height":{"unit":"em","size":1.3,"sizes":[]}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"},{"id":"86b7460","elType":"widget","settings":{"title":"Taking a look at the Flipverse","align":"left","title_color":"#000000","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Proxima Nova Alt Semi-Bold","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":22,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"600","typography_line_height":{"unit":"em","size":1.2,"sizes":[]},"header_size":"h3"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"heading"},{"id":"73f46da","elType":"widget","settings":{"editor":"<p>We thought the product could use some improvement in terms of its user interface and overall functionality.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Flipverse only works with Android phones right now.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>So iPhone users who want to shop in the metaverse will have to look elsewhere.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Mobile devices take too long to load, which also hurts the user experience.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>As a whole, the metaverse isn't very immersive, and if we're going to have a metaverse, we'd like it to be more immersive than it is now.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>We found that Flipkart using technology in Flipverse is an interesting experiment with a lot of room for growth.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>When compared to the high-end metaverse shopping experiences offered by companies like Gucci, Coca-Cola, and Zara.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p>","text_color":"#333333","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Proxima Nova Alt Reg","typography_font_size":{"unit":"px","size":18,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_weight":"400","typography_line_height":{"unit":"em","size":1.3,"sizes":[]}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false}]";}s:22:"_elementor_page_assets";a:1:{i:0;s:6:"a:0:{}";}s:26:"_yoast_wpseo_content_score";a:1:{i:0;s:2:"90";}s:43:"_yoast_wpseo_estimated-reading-time-minutes";a:1:{i:0;s:1:"4";}s:32:"_yoast_wpseo_wordproof_timestamp";a:1:{i:0;s:0:"";}s:12:"_wp_old_slug";a:9:{i:0;s:61:"some-important-things-to-know-about-axie-infinity-marketplace";i:1;s:50:"how-to-buy-and-sell-art-and-music-with-nft-in-2022";i:2;s:68:"how-is-blockchain-revolutionizing-the-mobile-app-development-process";i:3;s:49:"how-to-start-a-marketplace-development-business-2";i:4;s:50:"what-is-dapp-and-why-is-it-important-in-blockchain";i:5;s:36:"which-bitcoin-wallet-is-best-in-2022";i:6;s:42:"is-blockchain-better-than-coinbase-in-2022";i:7;s:50:"defi-nft-social-media-platform-development-in-2022";i:8;s:43:"decentralized-exchange-as-a-pancake-in-2022";}s:18:"_yoast_wpseo_title";a:1:{i:0;s:56:"Why did Flipkart choose Polygon to launch the metaverse?";}s:29:"_yoast_wpseo_primary_category";a:1:{i:0;s:2:"56";}s:20:"_yoast_wpseo_focuskw";a:1:{i:0;s:25:"Polygon in the metaverse?";}s:20:"_yoast_wpseo_linkdex";a:1:{i:0;s:2:"42";}s:13:"_thumbnail_id";a:1:{i:0;s:4:"6855";}s:14:"_elementor_css";a:1:{i:0;s:205:"a:6:{s:4:"time";i:1672838147;s:5:"fonts";a:2:{i:0;s:20:"Proxima Nova Alt Reg";i:1;s:26:"Proxima Nova Alt Semi-Bold";}s:5:"icons";a:0:{}s:20:"dynamic_elements_ids";a:0:{}s:6:"status";s:4:"file";i:0;s:0:"";}";}}}